</header>

<div class="modal fade" id="exampleModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="exampleModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog" style="min-width: 800px;" role="document">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-body">
                <div class="container" name="search bar" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div id="custom-search-input">
                                <div class="input-group col-md-12">
                                    <input type="text" class="form-control input-lg" placeholder="Search for a meal" />
                                    <span class="input-group-btn">
                                        <button class="btn btn-info btn-lg" type="button">
                                            <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-search"></i>
                                        </button>
                                    </span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="mealcard-container">
                    <div class="card card-default" name="meal card" style="max-width: 25vw;">
                        <div class="card-body card-5-7">
                            <div class="card-left">
                                <img class="meal-image" src="https://cdn.apartmenttherapy.info/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto,w_600,h_750,c_fit,fl_strip_profile/https://s3.amazonaws.com/pixtruder/original_images/39ee03d747ff0e93c946bdaaf07320e7679f0287" class="img-responsive">
                            </div>
                            <div class="card-right">
                                <div class="card-headings">30 min</div>
                                <div>Spaghetti</div>
                                <p class="card-p">Boil water in a large pot. To make sure pasta doesn't stick together, use at least 4 quarts of water for every pound of noodles.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card card-default" name="meal card" style="max-width: 25vw;">
                        <div class="card-body card-5-7">
                            <div class="card-left">
                                <img class="meal-image" src="https://www.thewholesomedish.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/Best-Lasagna-550.jpg" class="img-responsive">
                            </div>
                            <div class="card-right">
                                <div class="card-headings">45 min</div>
                                <div>Lasagna</div>
                                <p class="card-p">Preheat oven to 175 degrees C.In a large skillet, cook and stir ground beef until brown.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card card-default" name="meal card" style="max-width: 25vw;">
                        <div class="card-body card-5-7">
                            <div class="card-left">
                                <img class="meal-image" src="https://eatcaulipower.com/sites/default/files/product-images/Pizza-ThreeCheese_1.png" class="img-responsive">
                            </div>
                            <div class="card-right">
                                <div class="card-headings">25 min</div>
                                <div>Chease pizza</div>
                                <p class="card-p">Put a lot of chease on the pizza bottom and bake it at 200°C for untill it looks good.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card card-default" name="meal card" style="max-width: 25vw;">
                        <div class="card-body card-5-7">
                            <div class="card-left">
                                <img class="meal-image" src="https://www.diet.com/recipes/recipe_img/muesli-and-yogurt.jpg" class="img-responsive">
                            </div>
                            <div class="card-right">
                                <div class="card-headings">5 min</div>
                                <div>Musli & yogurt</div>
                                <p class="card-p">Pour the yougurt in a bowl and add musli, sugar spice and everything nice!<3</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card card-default" name="meal card" style="max-width: 25vw;">
                        <div class="card-body card-5-7">
                            <div class="card-left">
                                <img class="meal-image" src="https://www.bbcgoodfood.com/sites/default/files/styles/recipe/public/recipe/recipe-image/2017/05/chicken-fajitas.jpg?itok=zkc2flqY" class="img-responsive">
                            </div>
                            <div class="card-right">
                                <div class="card-headings">30 min</div>
                                <div>Fajita</div>
                                <p class="card-p">Cut the chicken in small pieces and fry on a pan. In the mean time cut the vegetables. Then put it all in the pancake.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card card-default" name="meal card" style="max-width: 25vw;">
                        <div class="card-body card-5-7">
                            <div class="card-left">
                                <img class="meal-image" src="https://imagesvc.timeincapp.com/v3/mm/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimg1.cookinglight.timeinc.net%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2F4_3_horizontal_-_1200x900%2Fpublic%2Fimage%2F2015%2F07%2Fmain%2F1508p73-clean-veggie-burgers.jpg%3Fitok%3DO9_SJh-8&w=450&c=sc&poi=face&q=85" class="img-responsive">
                            </div>
                            <div class="card-right">
                                <div class="card-headings">20 min</div>
                                <div>Vegan Hamburger</div>
                                <p class="card-p">Fry the veggie steak on the pan and slice vegetables. Make fries out of a sweet potato and cook in the oven.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary">Save changes</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

